# 🚀 Text Chat Engine (Backend)

A professional-grade, real-time messaging server built with **Node.js v24**. This backend serves as the core infrastructure for a high-performance chat application, featuring bi-directional communication, secure authentication, and persistent data storage.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Runtime:** Node.js v24 (ES Modules)
- **Framework:** Express.js
- **Real-time:** Socket.io (Room-based architecture)
- **Database:** MongoDB & Mongoose
- **Security:** JWT (JSON Web Tokens) & Bcrypt password hashing
- **Environment:** Dotenv for secure configuration

---

## ✨ Key Features

- **Real-time Messaging:** Low-latency text exchange using WebSockets.
- **Private Rooms:** Chat IDs generated for secure 1-on-1 conversations.
- **JWT Authentication:** Protected routes using custom middleware.
- **User Status:** Real-time online/offline status tracking.
- **Typing Indicators:** Visual feedback for active conversations.
- **Scalable Architecture:** Clean MVC (Model-View-Controller) structure.

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```text
src/
├── config/         # Database & Environment configs
├── controllers/    # Business & Auth Logic
├── middleware/     # Security (JWT) & Error handling
├── models/         # MongoDB Database Schemas
├── routes/         # API Endpoints
├── sockets/        # Real-time Socket.io logic
└── server.js       # Main Entry Point